        ties go to defender
        [lightsaber] = 2 success, other faces = 1, blank = 0
        if defender has 0 icons, it is still opposed and the attacker must roll 1 success
        "against a leader"
            captured leader only participates if the mission is against that leader, otherwise treated as if not in system
